tr: the cardinal compass point that is at 180 degrees

example.ex: It was a visit that took him to Mogadishu and southwards to Kismayo.
example.tran: 由于一次访问的缘故，他来到了摩加迪沙，又向南来到基斯马尤。

example.ex: Instead of her normal southward course towards Alexandria and home, she headed west.
example.tran: 她没有像往常一样选择前往亚历山大和回家的南行线路，而是向西走了。

gramarinfo.label: usu ADV after v, also n ADV
